They'll just shoo her out.

01:07:13.442 --> 01:07:17.276
So as long as she doesn't
do anything suspicious, she's fine.

01:08:29.651 --> 01:08:31.118
Oh, no.

01:08:31.252 --> 01:08:32.720
It's the chief of police.

01:08:33.921 --> 01:08:35.787
The chief of police!

01:08:45.334 --> 01:08:46.528
Thank you.

01:09:37.252 --> 01:09:39.243
I have, at different points in my life,

01:09:39.321 --> 01:09:43.256
quite literally sold ice to an Eskimo
and sand to an Arab.

01:09:43.325 --> 01:09:46.158
But I have no idea
what she could have said to that man

01:09:46.228 --> 01:09:49.197
to have sweet-talked her way
out of that castle.

01:09:49.264 --> 01:09:50.890
I could ask her.

01:09:50.966 --> 01:09:52.763
How obtuse.

01:09:54.970 --> 01:09:57.996
Let her sleep. Train doesn't leave until 8:00.

01:10:03.312 --> 01:10:04.802
That was real.

01:10:04.880 --> 01:10:06.211
Yeah, I know.

01:10:08.183 --> 01:10:09.207
Huh...

01:10:09.284 --> 01:10:11.149
Freaky scary.

