01:11:18.954 --> 01:11:21.980
<i>'Cause I know when I find it, my honey</i>

01:11:22.057 --> 01:11:25.754
<i>It's gonna make me feel good, yes</i>

01:11:27.596 --> 01:11:28.927
An apple.

01:11:30.365 --> 01:11:33.163
Yeah, it was part of an epiphany.

01:11:34.102 --> 01:11:36.366
<i>I love everything</i>

01:11:36.638 --> 01:11:39.402
<i>So don't it make you feel sad</i>

01:11:39.474 --> 01:11:42.375
<i>'Cause I'll drink to you, my baby</i>

01:11:42.444 --> 01:11:47.575
<i>I'll think to that Yes, I'll think to that</i>

