<i>Miles from nowhere</i>

01:11:58.326 --> 01:12:01.193
<i>Guess I'll take my time</i>

01:12:03.999 --> 01:12:05.227
<i>Oh, yeah</i>

01:12:06.635 --> 01:12:08.762
<i>To reach there</i>

01:12:12.774 --> 01:12:14.264
Mexico.

01:12:17.245 --> 01:12:19.975
Okay, we're rendezvousing
with the Argentina guys here,

01:12:20.048 --> 01:12:23.449
on a isolated beach
just south of the Hotel Tampico.

01:12:23.518 --> 01:12:24.815
A simple handoff.

01:12:24.920 --> 01:12:27.445
Penelope, you and Yueng Ling
stay with the car,

01:12:27.522 --> 01:12:30.286
Bloom and I will be doing the handing.

01:12:30.358 --> 01:12:31.916
You guys seem a little tense.

01:12:32.661 --> 01:12:36.461
Well, I'm not thrilled they set this in Mexico.

01:12:37.232 --> 01:12:40.599
There could be legitimate reasons,
but Mexico's...

01:12:40.669 --> 01:12:43.467
And I don't like to simplistically vilify
an entire country,

01:12:43.538 --> 01:12:45.733
but Mexico's a horrible place.

01:12:48.043 --> 01:12:49.806
So we'll be careful.

01:13:06.495 --> 01:13:09.259
This is gonna be dangerous tomorrow, right?

01:13:09.764 --> 01:13:11.231
Yeah.

01:13:13.468 --> 01:13:15.129
You should sleep at the hotel tonight.

01:13:15.270 --> 01:13:16.965
I'll stay with Stephen at the beach house.

01:13:17.038 --> 01:13:18.903
But you'll need sleep.

01:13:21.243 --> 01:13:24.804
I'm really happy right now. Are you?

01:13:27.282 --> 01:13:29.113
Right now I am.

01:13:29.784 --> 01:13:35.188
<i>I wanna be a smuggler</i>
<i>smuggle by day, drink by night</i>

01:13:35.457 --> 01:13:37.652
<i>Oh, hey, hey, hey, hey</i>

01:14:02.984 --> 01:14:05.214
The last box in our last con.

01:14:06.354 --> 01:14:07.821
How's it feel?

01:14:30.445 --> 01:14:32.106
Hey, what's up?

01:14:38.253 --> 01:14:40.050
Bloom! What?

01:14:51.399 --> 01:14:53.663
My brother and I are con men.

01:14:55.770 --> 01:14:57.135
And...

01:14:58.773 --> 01:15:02.504
Everything since you hit me
with your Lamborghini,

01:15:03.578 --> 01:15:05.273
it's all fake, it's all

01:15:07.248 --> 01:15:08.545
a con.

01:15:14.089 --> 01:15:16.614
Stephen's gone into town
to prep the Argentina actors.

01:15:16.691 --> 01:15:17.749
Money's in his place.

01:15:17.826 --> 01:15:21.023
Money? I don't want the money, let's just go.

01:15:27.669 --> 01:15:29.660
Come on, come on.

01:15:38.313 --> 01:15:40.804
You have to
switch it on at the base.

01:15:54.963 --> 01:15:57.193
So, I told her our whole play.

01:15:58.833 --> 01:16:01.563
And I'm here to take her money back.

01:16:03.204 --> 01:16:05.331
How does that make you feel?

01:16:07.275 --> 01:16:08.640
Disappointed.

01:16:08.710 --> 01:16:10.507
This isn't the ending you wanted?

01:16:11.946 --> 01:16:15.575
What does that matter?
This is the way it ends now.

01:16:16.551 --> 01:16:19.247
So I might as well just get it over with.

01:16:19.320 --> 01:16:20.514
- Where's the money?
- I ate it.

01:16:20.588 --> 01:16:22.556
- Give me the money, Stephen.
- No.

01:16:22.624 --> 01:16:23.886
I don't want the money.

01:16:23.958 --> 01:16:26.119
He's not gonna keep a single piece of you.
Give me the money.

01:16:26.194 --> 01:16:29.391
I'm sorry you fell in love with her.
She's a mark.

01:16:29.564 --> 01:16:32.362
And all of this, all of it is just a con.

01:16:33.168 --> 01:16:34.499
And every moment you share with her,

01:16:34.569 --> 01:16:37.094
you're just playing the part
of a man falling in love.

01:16:37.172 --> 01:16:39.766
That's what you're afraid of, isn't it?

01:16:40.508 --> 01:16:42.567
That you don't know the difference.

01:16:42.644 --> 01:16:44.771
Or maybe that there really is no difference.

01:16:44.846 --> 01:16:46.780
That that's what love is, right?

01:16:46.848 --> 01:16:49.408
Okay, we're leaving.

01:16:49.651 --> 01:16:50.982
No.

01:16:51.686 --> 01:16:53.779
You're too scared to leave.

01:16:54.022 --> 01:16:56.286
You're too scared to ride off into the sunset,

01:16:56.357 --> 01:16:58.257
because real sunsets might be beautiful

01:16:58.326 --> 01:17:00.988
but they turn into dark, uncertain nights.

01:17:01.529 --> 01:17:05.829
No, you're not ready,
otherwise you wouldn't be here right now.

01:17:08.136 --> 01:17:10.866
The money is in my bedroom.
It's right behind me.

01:17:10.939 --> 01:17:15.035
But in my story you don't get the money
or the sunset or the girl.

01:17:18.046 --> 01:17:19.274
Bloom,

01:17:21.316 --> 01:17:22.874
let's just go.

01:17:24.385 --> 01:17:25.579
Please.

