Tastes like tinfoil.

01:18:26.848 --> 01:18:28.281
I'm sorry.

01:18:32.620 --> 01:18:34.451
Shh. Shh. Shh.

01:18:39.194 --> 01:18:40.889
Get out of here.

01:18:42.630 --> 01:18:44.461
Take the car and go.

01:18:46.267 --> 01:18:48.167
I'm not going anywhere.

01:20:25.199 --> 01:20:31.069
<i>The storm is passed</i>
<i>There is peace at last</i>

01:20:31.673 --> 01:20:36.508
<i>I've spent my whole life sleeping</i>

01:20:37.512 --> 01:20:41.107
<i>Now there's not a sound</i>

01:20:41.182 --> 01:20:45.744
<i>No one to be found anywhere</i>

01:20:50.458 --> 01:20:56.260
